ilmbase: ilmbase (ILM Thread Abstraction Library)
ilmbase:
ilmbase: IlmThread is a pthread abstraction library for use with OpenEXR and 
ilmbase: other software packages. It also includes Imath, which implements 2D 
ilmbase: and 3D vectors, 3x3 and 4x4 matrices, quaternions and other useful 2D 
ilmbase: and 3D math functions, as well as Iex, an exception-handling library.
ilmbase: The ILMbase software distribution is now licensed under the modified 
ilmbase: BSD license.
